    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《无光之晓》是一部黑暗、心理与哲学交织的视觉恐怖小说，呈现出阴森而美丽的伪ASCII艺术风格。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她在远离尘嚣的山间小屋寻得栖所，欲摆脱那挥之不去的思绪纷扰。在此静谧孤寂之地，万籁俱寂，唯有森林间穿梭的寒风发出令人不安的低语，使她辗转难眠。在漫漫长夜中，那无边的寂静仿佛已悄然化为实质的存在。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《无光之晓》以匠心独运之法引导玩家步入自我探索的深渊，巧妙融合心理学与哲学元素，编织出一段模糊现实与虚构边界的沉浸式体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145620/extras/6ea39b5f9e48109ad5c8cefd6895e96b.gif?t=1767956222\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145620/extras/6ea39b5f9e48109ad5c8cefd6895e96b.poster.avif?t=1767956222\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >艺术风格与音效皆出自匠心独运之手，饱含细腻用心与情感。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可自由切换的色彩配置、质感纹理及画面边框。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸于扣人心弦的叙事之中，体验现实与虚构交织的朦胧边界。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索精微深刻的哲学思考与心灵自省。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >芬兰原创精心打造。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145620/extras/7a40b53799d3006d54954db1a8bd5772.poster.avif?t=1767956222\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145620/extras/7a40b53799d3006d54954db1a8bd5772.webm?t=1767956222\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >社区特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《无光之晓》支持导入玩家自制本地化语言包！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >创作专属个性化调色板、边框与纹理！*</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《无光之晓》支持导入外部语音表演！*</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145620/extras/a8adb2dc18d7b757b6c1b6c5a2edf712.gif?t=1767956222\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145620/extras/a8adb2dc18d7b757b6c1b6c5a2edf712.poster.avif?t=1767956222\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>*创作调色板、边框与纹理需使用图像处理软件。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>*外部语音需使用音频处理软件。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>*详细指南请参阅游戏目录中的技术文档。</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145620/extras/126b2f08be41dce2716830069dfc10ba.apng?t=1767956222\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145620/extras/126b2f08be41dce2716830069dfc10ba.poster.avif?t=1767956222\" class=\"bb_img\" width=512 height=64 /></picture></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>媒体、内容创作者与影响力人士专用宣传资料包可在官方网站获取。</i></p>",
